snippet.title: Super Mario Bros. Next - 2022 Trailer [Unofficial Mod]
snippet.description:
Super Mario Bros. Next is an upcoming single-player mod for New Super Mario Bros. 2 on the Nintendo 3DS, developed by longtime fans of the NSMB series. Featuring nine full-length worlds to explore, as well as a plethora of brand new enemies, mechanics, and power-ups, it promises to be quite the exciting adventure!

Website: http://smbnext.net
Discord Server: https://smbnext.net/discord/
